item.title: CVE-2024-37065|2024-06-04T12:03:19.459Z -- Skops-dev -- Skops
item.description: Deserialization of untrusted data can occur in versions 0.6 or newer of the skops python library, enabling a maliciously crafted model to run arbitrary code on an end user's system when loaded.
